://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/2b/2c/618795_kS9Rt.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/2b/2c/618795_kS9Rt.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/2b/2c/618795_kS9Rt.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/2b/2c/618795_kS9Rt.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/2b/2c/618795_kS9Rt.jpg"},"summary":"◤初星コミュ  TV放送決定！◢\r\n\r\nゲーム内の初星コミュを一部再編集した\r\n『学園アイドルマスター Story of Re;IRIS』が\r\nTOKYO MXにて、2026年１月１日(木)にTV放送決定\r\n\r\n✦キャスト特別番組\r\n✦学園アイドルマスター Story of Re;IRIS\r\nの特別な2本立て放送です✨\r\n\r\nキャスト特別番組は『TVer』でも配信しますよ?\r\n\r\nアイドル養成学校である初星学園に所属する3人のアイドルとプロデューサの出会いが起こす、青春と挫折と葛藤を描いた奇跡の物語。さらに！本編の放送に追加して、出演声優による学マス入門特別番組も！物語の一挙放送と、華やかなスタジオ特番を通して、『学園アイドルマスター』の世界をたっぷり味わえる新春6時間スペシャルです。","name":"学園アイドルマスター Story of Re;IRIS","name_cn":"学园偶像大师 Story of Re;IRIS","tags":[{"name":"游戏改","count":98,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026年1月","count":82,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":80,"total_cont":0},{"name":"偶像","count":74,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026","count":70,"total_cont":0},{"name":"偶像大师","count":70,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":64,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":41,"total_cont":0},{"name":"3D","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"IM@S","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"音乐","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"京极尚彦","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"伏见司","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"QualiArts","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"伏見つかさ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"京極尚彦","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026冬","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"待标","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WEB","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"29-100","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"三渲二","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"成长","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新祐樹","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"20s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常",